    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a bit of road noise at higher speeds. The exterior has various scuffs, small dents, and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows noticeable wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. It has been recently serviced for basic maintenance, but a buyer should expect to address some suspension bushings and cosmetic touch-ups in the near future.",
