    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical attention, including engine diagnostics and a full suspension overhaul, before it can be considered roadworthy. The exterior shows its age and neglect with substantial body damage, including deep scratches, noticeable rust spots on the wheel wells, and a cracked windshield. Inside, the cabin shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and several non-functioning electronic components. This car is ideal only for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a major restoration project or as a donor vehicle for spare parts.",
