    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly pristine condition. This specimen has been maintained to the highest standards, reflecting a level of care usually reserved for private collections. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, every detail speaks to its showroom-quality pedigree. Rigorously inspected and ready for the most discerning driver, this is more than a car\u2014it is a testament to automotive excellence and a rare find for the serious buyer.",
      "price": 46500.0,
